“Sterilis is an industry disrupter that will profoundly change the way medical waste is managed. No longer is it acceptable to package, store and transport the massive quantities of medical waste generated by the United States medical system to a few processing plants scattered across the country,”


- Dr. Seth Yellin - Marietta Facial Plastic Surgery, Laser & Aesthetics Center
“Sterilis is a simple solution that allowed us to eliminate the storage of hazardous medical waste along with the record keeping. It also greatly reduced the cost of disposing of our regulated materials. It is a win, win, win for any practice or surgical center that generates medical waste! ”


- Dr. Michael Oats - Ophthalmic Consultants of Boston
“The inherent liability and risks of trucking contaminated waste across the country for disposal, the fossil fuel consumed in the process, and the greenhouse gases generated make this mode of medical waste disposal both outdated and expensive. By treating contaminated medical waste of all kinds on site, at the location where it is created, and then disposing of the treated material as regular trash, medical facilities will lower their costs, our roads will be less crowded and safer and the environment will benefit. Everybody wins!”


- Dr. Seth Yellin - Marietta Facial Plastic Surgery, Laser & Aesthetics Center

Please contact us for more information on the features and benefits of Sterilis, LLC.

        The Sterilis System provides ease of use, safety, convenience and cost savings features in one remarkable device!

